{"tid":1900012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日外相：期待中國疫情盡快平息 感謝中國提供醫療物資","createTime":"2020-02-27T03:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T05:31:50.000Z","uid":91914,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0362358975a33880a0642001b92c5f707b0a860e","tid":1900012,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:27:50.000Z","msg":"屌你日本政府真係好撚失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n王毅與茂木敏充通話　稱關注日本疫情願意提供幫助<br />\n<br />\n國務委員兼外交部長王毅與日本外相茂木敏充通電話。王毅表示，中方防控新型肺炎疫情穩步向好，讚賞日方一開始就同中國站在一起，感謝日本給予的支持和幫助。中方關注日本的疫情，已經根據日方需求提供必要醫療防護物資，願意繼續提供幫助。茂木敏充期待中國疫情盡快平息，又感謝中方提供醫療物資，強調日本政府已經制定應對方針，防止疫情蔓延。共同社報道，國家主席習近平原定4月到日本國事訪問，兩國外長在通話中，確認將繼續密切溝通，認為需要讓訪問富有成果。<br />\n<br />\n2020-02-27 10:25:03"},{"pid":"a546a47bf8617c92eb7a5932316367c698d25023","tid":1900012,"uid":91914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:28:08.000Z","msg":"RTHK"},{"pid":"fc09f4e01fd668097c70ef0f2f3413369f738b09","tid":1900012,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:28:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"f433eba3e56320dc2d1fca81f0cd14bfeef19e50","tid":1900012,"uid":134571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"屌都廢事"},{"pid":"790aa9a62f1400f9feb1359a8e440942cf0a02ef","tid":1900012,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:29:57.000Z","msg":"日本：繼續奶奶奶搞奧運啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2980194/org/35c2ec6e0a753f2eb2bd9b2ca7178a3e.JPG/c23r_aeUgVLBiohZrozVHviUOR6yI1nowTAN8sEwDfI?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2980194%2Forg%2F35c2ec6e0a753f2eb2bd9b2ca7178a3e.JPG%2Fc23r_aeUgVLBiohZrozVHviUOR6yI1nowTAN8sEwDfI%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=5e80ca3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57a37fac163f65a10e2ed085518826676410a257","tid":1900012,"uid